{"tid":580613,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"咁大個女第一個人自由行，想問下旅遊保係咪一定要買？","createTime":"2018-03-04T15:40:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T05:42:09.000Z","uid":173133,"like":1,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"6aa518ba2fbc312ce742b41130978357a6123800","tid":580613,"uid":173133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T15:40:16.000Z","msg":"以前同屋企人去旅行都係跟團，咩都唔洗搞。 <br />\n但今次自己一個人去台灣5日自由行，想慳返少少，5日旅遊保最平都要$百幾二百蚊，買左又好似冇咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n所以想問下巴絲打去旅行既話，一定會買旅遊保？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4329a2f2bdb0e7a9d14406ce8f0f6b07fd2b19c","tid":580613,"uid":128949,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"6aa518ba2fbc312ce742b41130978357a6123800","tid":580613,"uid":173133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T15:40:16.000Z","msg":"以前同屋企人去旅行都係跟團，咩都唔洗搞。 <br />\n但今次自己一個人去台灣5日自由行，想慳返少少，5日旅遊保最平都要$百幾二百蚊，買左又好似冇咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n所以想問下巴絲打去旅行既話，一定會買旅遊保？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T15:42:47.000Z","msg":"買 <br />\n慳極都唔好慳旅遊保<br />\n去得旅行就唔好慳啦"},{"pid":"9f31c2557bcc96d80945888b26a8089d25def764","tid":580613,"uid":155172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T15:43:23.000Z","msg":"緊係買啦"},{"pid":"9eddce6dea7386172392328c81b5cf87c0d9a69b","tid":580613,"uid":149825,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T15:43:34.000Z","msg":"你跟中銀買5,6日最平個款都係百幾二百姐"},{"pid":"aa45b8a9b3a71e58b9d5f9b48ce3b4a499caffa9","tid":580613,"uid":156547,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T15:44:58.000Z","msg":"有咩事屋企有錢解決就唔使買"},{"pid":"ff27e0740e5c3aa196caf614fd3f6d7a457db84d","tid":580613,"uid":92643,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T15:46:32.000Z","msg":"保險呢就無事你會覺得買黎無咩用,但有事你會後悔點解買咁細 <img src=\"